Message: Hi, I’m the NewsBreak Ad Assistant. How can I help?
Hello! How can I assist you today?
how can I start max conversion value

To start maximizing conversion value, you can follow these steps:
1. Use the 'Go test' feature at the bottom of the page to ensure your tracking implementation is successful.
2. Save and proceed once you see 'Test result: successful.'
3. After successfully testing the tracking implementation and creating your event, save the changes.
4. Proceed with setting up your ad.
For more detailed information, you can refer to this article: [Introduction to Maximize Conversions](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/20624355375117-Introduction-to-Maximize-Conversions). If you have any questions, feel free to contact adsupport@newsbreak.com.
is it eligible for leads gen

Maximize Conversions is generally used for generating as many conversions as possible, which can include lead generation. It's a good fit for performance advertisers who have clearly defined performance goals and seek to maximize their return on investment. For more details, you can check out the article [Introduction to Maximize Conversions](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/20624355375117-Introduction-to-Maximize-Conversions).
what'ts the difference between max conversion and max conversion value

Maximize Conversions focuses on getting the highest number of conversions within your specified daily budget, while Maximize Conversion Value aims to get the highest total conversion value within your budget. Essentially, Maximize Conversions is about quantity, and Maximize Conversion Value is about the quality or value of those conversions. For more details on these strategies, you can refer to this article: [How to choose a bidding strategy](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/21344263367053-How-to-choose-a-bidding-strategy).
电商适合什么类型的出价

对于电商来说，选择合适的出价策略非常重要。一般来说，如果你希望在控制成本的同时获得尽可能多的转化，可以选择“目标每次转化费用（tCPA）”出价策略。如果你的目标是最大化转化数量，可以选择“最大化转化（Maximize Conversions）”出价策略。此外，如果你希望在预算范围内获得最高的总转化价值，可以选择“最大化转化价值（Maximize Conversion Value）”出价策略。更多详细信息可以参考这篇文章：[如何选择出价策略](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/21344263367053-How-to-choose-a-bidding-strategy)。
